Description: Terminal workspace manager for AI coding agents (DTK frontend)
 herdr is a terminal workspace manager designed for AI coding agents.
 It provides workspace, tab, and pane management with a client-server
 architecture.
 .
 This package contains the DTK GUI frontend that embeds the herdr
 terminal client and auto-downloads the herdr binary on first launch.
